From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Disable Field Trials Seed

Disables the fetch of the seed for Google's field trial and variations system.

---
 components/variations/variations_seed_store.cc | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/components/variations/variations_seed_store.cc b/components/variations/variations_seed_store.cc
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/components/variations/variations_seed_store.cc
+++ b/components/variations/variations_seed_store.cc
@@ -20,6 +20,10 @@

 namespace variations {

+bool VariationsSeedStore::StoreSeed(const std::string& seed_data) {
+  return false; // Nickel: Never store Google's experiment seeds
+}
+
 bool VariationsSeedStore::LoadSeed(VariationsSeed* seed) {
   return false;
 }
--
